# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#               Git ignore everything except these folders/files
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Ignore all files by default
*

# Un-ignore version control settings
!.gitignore

# Un-ignore package descriptor
!package.json

# Un-ignore your AppsFlyer SDK folder and all its contents
!AppsFlyer/
!AppsFlyer/**

# Un-ignore your Purchase Connector folder and all its contents
!AppsFlyerPurchaseConnector/
!AppsFlyerPurchaseConnector/**

# Un-ignore your custom runtime scripts folder (if any)
!Runtime/
!Runtime/**

# If you later add other top-level files you want to include,
# add explicit !<filename> lines here.

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Note:
# This setup will keep only:
#   • AppsFlyer/*
#   • AppsFlyerPurchaseConnector/*
#   • Runtime/*
#   • package.json
#   • .gitignore
# in your repo. Everything else will be ignored.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────